Class NameExpression

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitable, java.lang.Comparable<ASTNode>

    public class NameExpression
extends Expression
    A class representing Java identifiers over several categories. These identifiers may be qualified by another NameExpression, yet each NameExpression represents a logically atomic name e.g. foo
